description.text: Take what you can. Give nothing back! Join Jack and his crew in the Pirates of the Caribbean Mash-up, featuring all of your favorite rogues and rascals. Plot a course from Tortuga to Shipwreck Cove and all the way down to Davy Jonesâ€™ Locker. This is the day you will always remember as the day you sailed with Captain Jack Sparrow.
